    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pixeria, An all-in-one Pixel MMO</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes, you heard right. What you miss and what you wish you had met in a single universe. <strong>Create your own island</strong>, and enjoy endless adventures with those around you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/74ce7fce1625e7b3c01ee58a6ec3f8a7.poster.avif?t=1749641636\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/74ce7fce1625e7b3c01ee58a6ec3f8a7.webm?t=1749641636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/74ce7fce1625e7b3c01ee58a6ec3f8a7.mp4?t=1749641636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On a deserted island, with the sky and the waves as your companions, you can <strong>become a gardener and harvest your own crops</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/54aafe51b6137560f5ac965f1a7442db.poster.avif?t=1749641636\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/54aafe51b6137560f5ac965f1a7442db.webm?t=1749641636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/54aafe51b6137560f5ac965f1a7442db.mp4?t=1749641636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through various missions, you can <strong>earn valuable materials and develop your character</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/c5bb06c0655fbc8d3be1f181b9d10652.poster.avif?t=1749641636\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/c5bb06c0655fbc8d3be1f181b9d10652.webm?t=1749641636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/c5bb06c0655fbc8d3be1f181b9d10652.mp4?t=1749641636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On another day when you are bored, you can <strong>take care of your animals or even beekeeping</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/f4800182673736b65537b7279bf6cb3f.poster.avif?t=1749641636\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/f4800182673736b65537b7279bf6cb3f.webm?t=1749641636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/f4800182673736b65537b7279bf6cb3f.mp4?t=1749641636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Believing that power lies in the economy, you can <strong>find your way to wealth through trading</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Knowing that the real diamonds are underground,  you can <strong>become a professional miner</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In short, <strong>you can do whatever you really want</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixeria offers you the chance to create a universe of your own choosing, making new friends and creating your best memories here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join us and enjoy unlimited adventures!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Trading</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Mining</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Farming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Ranching</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Socializing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fishing</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Also Note That:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>You can play from anywhere, anytime</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>Pixeria is still in early development, join our discord to experience the beta tests.</i></p></li></ul>",
